        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[dYdX 转型成公共利益公司，不会从 V4 产生交易费收入！主网预计本月推出]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">dYdX V4 开发至今已过了一年多的时间，其创办人 Antonio Juliano 曾表示主网预计 10 月推出。另外，他还于近日宣布，dYdX 已转型成公共利益公司，不会从 V4 产生交易收入。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-becomes-a-public-benefit-corporation#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-652f86f0cd53b"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-652f86f0cd53b"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-becomes-a-public-benefit-corporation/#dYdX_V4_%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88_10_%E6%9C%88%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA" title="dYdX V4 持续测试中，主网预计 10 月推出">dYdX V4 持续测试中，主网预计 10 月推出</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-becomes-a-public-benefit-corporation/#dYdX_%E8%BD%89%E5%9E%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%9E_V4_%E7%94%A2%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5" title="dYdX 转型公共利益公司，不从&nbsp;V4 产生交易收入">dYdX 转型公共利益公司，不从&nbsp;V4 产生交易收入</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="dYdX_V4_%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88_10_%E6%9C%88%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA"></span>dYdX V4 持续测试中，主网预计 10 月推出<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>根据先前报导，以太坊 L2 上的衍生品交易所 dYdX 将在未来推出的 V4 版本把协议迁移至 Cosmos 生态，并基于 Cosmos SDK 开发「dYdX 链」。</p><p>(完整阅读：<a href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-token-migration" target="_blank" rel="noopener">dYdX V4 要来了？DYDX 代币迁移提案通过！将离开以太坊入驻「dYdX 链」</a>)</p><p>目前，dYdX 链测试网 3 已经关闭，本周晚些将上线测试网 4。另外，在 CoinDesk 对 dYdX 创办人 Antonio Juliano 的<a href="https://www.coindesk.com/tech/2023/09/20/we-cant-build-something-like-this-on-ethereum-says-dydx-founder-as-mainnet-nears/?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=editorial&amp;utm_term=organic&amp;utm_campaign=coindesk_main&amp;utm_medium=social" target="_blank" rel="noopener">采访</a>中，Antonio 预计 dYdX 链主网预计会于 10 月推出。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">We’re winding down the dYdX Chain Testnet 3 today at 17:00 UTC and will relaunch Testnet 4 later this week!</p><p>Until then, the Testnet will be unavailable 🫡</p><p>— dYdX (@dYdX) <a href="https://twitter.com/dYdX/status/1713923995140243468?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 16, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="dYdX_%E8%BD%89%E5%9E%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%9E_V4_%E7%94%A2%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5"></span>dYdX 转型公共利益公司，不从&nbsp;V4 产生交易收入<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>在 dYdX 链主网即将发布之际，创办人 Antonio 在 X 上宣布重大消息。Antonio 表示 dYdX 交易公司已正式更新其章程，成为一间公共利益 (Public Benefit) 公司。&nbsp;</p><p class="content">「作为开源软体开发商，我们不会营运或从 dYdX V4 产生交易费收入，我们认真地与社群保持一致。」</p><p>Antonio 补充，尽管作为一间公共利益公司，dYdX 仍将继续作为一家盈利公司营运。然而，这会使他和董事会不仅是为了极大化股东价值而行动，同时也为了公共利益而行动。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">dYdX Trading Inc. has officially updated its charter to become a Public Benefit Corporation</p><p>As open source software developers, we will not operate or generate trading fee revenue from dYdX v4. We are serious about being as aligned as possible with the community 🤝</p><p>— Antonio | dYdX (@AntonioMJuliano) <a href="https://twitter.com/AntonioMJuliano/status/1714251418675155435?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 17, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
]]>
            </description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 05:13:52 GMT</pubDate>
